              Lot: 23
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="home_details">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-6 col-md-6 col-lg-6">
                <p class="home_details__text">
                  Price: $123,000<br/>
                  Status: For Sale<br/>
                  Community: Lagohone
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-6 col-md-6 col-lg-6">
                <p class="home_details__text">
                  SQ FT: 2,400<br/>
                  Bedrooms: 4<br/>
                  Bathrooms: 2.5<br/>Garages: 1
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-12 view_btn">
